  +navbar("index")
  section#home-screen-1
    .screen-container
      .pure-g
        .pure-u-1.pure-u-md-1-2
          .description-text
            .question
              |We've heard these too many times!!...
            ul.fa-ul
              li #[i.fa-li.fa.fa-comment] So many buzz news that we can't remember what's important.
              li #[i.fa-li.fa.fa-comment] So many disturbing notifications that we can't focus on learning.
              li #[i.fa-li.fa.fa-comment] So many personalized filters that we can't expand our horizons.
            
        .pure-u-1.pure-u-md-1-2
          .description-text
            .question
              |So how do we actually make better social media ?
            |WorthWhileWeb is a movement to imagine and promote online environments so enriching you'll never say the internet is a waste of time again.
          .btn-cont
            input(type="email" placeholder="Weekly Newsletter")
            button.btn
              a(href="" target="_blank") Subscribe
          .description-text
            .newsletter-desc
              |Absolutely No Spam.
              br
              |Only worthwhile initiatives, tips, &amp; reads.
              br
              |On a weekly basis.
